    %% 1:N Relationships
    A -->|has many| AA
    A -->|has many| W
    A -->|has many| MS
    A -->|referenced by| SL
    A -->|linked to| INV
    A -->|linked to| PO
    
    %% M:N Relationships
    SL -.multiple assignments.- A
    INV -.contains.- A
    PO -.contains.- A
    
    %% Foreign Key references
    V -->|supplies| INV
    V -->|supplies| PO
    V -->|maintains| MS
    V -->|provides warranty| W
    
    U -->|owns| A
    U -->|assigned| AA
    U -->|approves| AA
    U -->|approves| INV
    U -->|approves| PO
    U -->|changes recorded| AUD
    
    CP -->|governs| A
    
